</div></div>
<div class="infobox infobox_v3 large"><div class="entete defaut" style="background-color:#EEEEFF;color:#000000"><div>Arthur Ashkin</div></div><div><div class="images" style="padding:2px 0"><a href="/wiki/Fichier:Arthur_Ashkin_EM1B5678_(44417135450).jpg" class="image"><img alt="Image dans Infobox." src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1d/Arthur_Ashkin_EM1B5678_%2844417135450%29.jpg/260px-Arthur_Ashkin_EM1B5678_%2844417135450%29.jpg" decoding="async" width="260" height="347" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1d/Arthur_Ashkin_EM1B5678_%2844417135450%29.jpg/390px-Arthur_Ashkin_EM1B5678_%2844417135450%29.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1d/Arthur_Ashkin_EM1B5678_%2844417135450%29.jpg/520px-Arthur_Ashkin_EM1B5678_%2844417135450%29.jpg 2x" data-file-width="3618" data-file-height="4824" /></a></div></div><table><caption style="color:#000000;text-align:center;background-color:#EEEEFF">Biographie</caption><tbody><tr class=""><th scope="row">Naissance</th><td class=""><div>
