168265762">Gemeinsame Normdatei</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://data.bibliotheken.nl/id/thes/p32073479X">Bibliothèque royale des Pays-Bas</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://aut.nkp.cz/xx0031123">Bibliothèque nationale tchèque</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.worldcat.org/identities/lccn-no2007037973">WorldCat Id</a></span></li><li><span class="nowrap uid noarchive"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.worldcat.org/identities/lccn-no2007-037973">WorldCat</a></span></li></ul></div></li>
